com.bachelor_project.interpreterast.types

Class LockedPointer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bachelor_project.interpreterast.types.LockedPointer

  • public class LockedPointer
extends Object
    A wrapper that restricts access to objects, used to implement shared variables.
    Author:
    Alexandru Babeanu

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static long NO_OWNER
      The owner id of a variable whose lock is not currently held by any thread.

        public Object getValue()
                throws RuntimeException
        Returns the underlying object (the value of the shared variable).
        Returns:

              throws RuntimeException
        Changes the value of the shared variable.

      • sameStructure

        public boolean sameStructure(LockedPointer other)
        Checks whether another LockedPointer is part of the same structure. LockedPointer objects from the same structure tree will share the LockedPointer.OwnerId object. LockedPointer objects from different structures may have the same LockedPointer.OwnerId value, but will have different objects.
        Parameters:
        other - the other LockedPointer object
        Returns:
        true if other is part of the same structure, false otherwise.
